snippets.title: datalabeling createDataset Sample
snippets.description: Creates dataset. If success return a Dataset resource.

snippets.title: datalabeling getDataset Sample
snippets.description: Gets dataset by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling listDatasets Sample
snippets.description: Lists datasets under a project. Pagination is supported.

snippets.title: datalabeling deleteDataset Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a dataset by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling importData Sample
snippets.description: Imports data into dataset based on source locations defined in request. It can be called multiple times for the same dataset. Each dataset can only have one long running operation running on it. For example, no labeling task (also long running operation) can be started while importing is still ongoing. Vice versa.

snippets.title: datalabeling exportData Sample
snippets.description: Exports data and annotations from dataset.

snippets.title: datalabeling getDataItem Sample
snippets.description: Gets a data item in a dataset by resource name. This API can be called after data are imported into dataset.

snippets.title: datalabeling listDataItems Sample
snippets.description: Lists data items in a dataset. This API can be called after data are imported into dataset. Pagination is supported.

snippets.title: datalabeling getAnnotatedDataset Sample
snippets.description: Gets an annotated dataset by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling listAnnotatedDatasets Sample
snippets.description: Lists annotated datasets for a dataset. Pagination is supported.

snippets.title: datalabeling deleteAnnotatedDataset Sample
snippets.description: Deletes an annotated dataset by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling labelImage Sample
snippets.description: Starts a labeling task for image. The type of image labeling task is configured by feature in the request.

snippets.title: datalabeling labelVideo Sample
snippets.description: Starts a labeling task for video. The type of video labeling task is configured by feature in the request.

snippets.title: datalabeling labelText Sample
snippets.description: Starts a labeling task for text. The type of text labeling task is configured by feature in the request.

snippets.title: datalabeling getExample Sample
snippets.description: Gets an example by resource name, including both data and annotation.

snippets.title: datalabeling listExamples Sample
snippets.description: Lists examples in an annotated dataset. Pagination is supported.

snippets.title: datalabeling createAnnotationSpecSet Sample
snippets.description: Creates an annotation spec set by providing a set of labels.

snippets.title: datalabeling getAnnotationSpecSet Sample
snippets.description: Gets an annotation spec set by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling listAnnotationSpecSets Sample
snippets.description: Lists annotation spec sets for a project. Pagination is supported.

snippets.title: datalabeling deleteAnnotationSpecSet Sample
snippets.description: Deletes an annotation spec set by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling createInstruction Sample
snippets.description: Creates an instruction for how data should be labeled.

snippets.title: datalabeling getInstruction Sample
snippets.description: Gets an instruction by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling listInstructions Sample
snippets.description: Lists instructions for a project. Pagination is supported.

snippets.title: datalabeling deleteInstruction Sample
snippets.description: Deletes an instruction object by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling getEvaluation Sample
snippets.description: Gets an evaluation by resource name (to search, use [projects.evaluations.search][google.cloud.datalabeling.v1beta1.DataLabelingService.SearchEvaluations]).

snippets.title: datalabeling searchEvaluations Sample
snippets.description: Searches [evaluations][google.cloud.datalabeling.v1beta1.Evaluation] within a project.

snippets.title: datalabeling searchExampleComparisons Sample
snippets.description: Searches example comparisons from an evaluation. The return format is a list of example comparisons that show ground truth and prediction(s) for a single input. Search by providing an evaluation ID.

snippets.title: datalabeling createEvaluationJob Sample
snippets.description: Creates an evaluation job.

snippets.title: datalabeling updateEvaluationJob Sample
snippets.description: Updates an evaluation job. You can only update certain fields of the job's [EvaluationJobConfig][google.cloud.datalabeling.v1beta1.EvaluationJobConfig]: `humanAnnotationConfig.instruction`, `exampleCount`, and `exampleSamplePercentage`. If you want to change any other aspect of the evaluation job, you must delete the job and create a new one.

snippets.title: datalabeling getEvaluationJob Sample
snippets.description: Gets an evaluation job by resource name.

snippets.title: datalabeling pauseEvaluationJob Sample
snippets.description: Pauses an evaluation job. Pausing an evaluation job that is already in a `PAUSED` state is a no-op.

snippets.title: datalabeling resumeEvaluationJob Sample
snippets.description: Resumes a paused evaluation job. A deleted evaluation job can't be resumed. Resuming a running or scheduled evaluation job is a no-op.

snippets.title: datalabeling deleteEvaluationJob Sample
snippets.description: Stops and deletes an evaluation job.

snippets.title: datalabeling listEvaluationJobs Sample
snippets.description: Lists all evaluation jobs within a project with possible filters. Pagination is supported.
